exercises.name: Push-up
exercises.instructions: Start in a plank position, hands shoulder-width apart, elbows close to the body. Lower your body until your chest almost touches the floor, then push yourself back to the start position.

exercises.name: Squat
exercises.instructions: Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart. Bend your knees and lower your body as if sitting in a chair. Keep your back straight and chest up. Return to the starting position.

exercises.name: Deadlift
exercises.instructions: Stand with your feet hip-width apart, grip the barbell with both hands. With your back straight, hinge at the hips and lift the barbell while keeping it close to your body.

exercises.name: Plank
exercises.instructions: Start in a push-up position but with your forearms on the ground. Keep your body in a straight line from head to heels and hold the position.

exercises.name: Bicep Curl
exercises.instructions: Hold a dumbbell in each hand with palms facing forward. Curl the weights toward your shoulders while keeping your elbows close to your body. Lower back to the starting position.

exercises.name: Lunges
exercises.instructions: Step forward with one leg and lower your body until both knees are at 90-degree angles. Push back to the starting position and repeat with the other leg.

exercises.name: Pull-up
exercises.instructions: Grab the pull-up bar with your palms facing forward and hands slightly wider than shoulder-width apart. Pull your chin above the bar, then lower back down.

exercises.name: Dumbbell Bench Press
exercises.instructions: Lie on a bench with a dumbbell in each hand. Lower the dumbbells to chest level, then press them back up to the starting position.

exercises.name: Mountain Climbers
exercises.instructions: Start in a push-up position. Drive one knee towards your chest and then quickly switch legs, as if running in place while maintaining a plank position.

exercises.name: Russian Twist
exercises.instructions: Sit on the floor with knees bent and feet flat. Lean back slightly and twist your torso from side to side while keeping your arms extended in front of you.

exercises.name: Push-ups
exercises.instructions: Lower your body until your chest nearly touches the floor and then push yourself back up.

exercises.name: Squats
exercises.instructions: Stand with feet shoulder-width apart, lower hips down and back, then return to standing.

exercises.name: Plank
exercises.instructions: Hold your body in a straight line, supported by your forearms and toes.

exercises.name: Jumping Jacks
exercises.instructions: Jump while spreading your legs and arms, then return to starting position.

exercises.name: Mountain Climbers
exercises.instructions: Start in a push-up position and alternate bringing knees to your chest quickly.

exercises.name: Burpees
exercises.instructions: Squat, kick back into a plank, do a push-up, return to squat and jump.

exercises.name: Bicycle Crunches
exercises.instructions: Lie on your back and alternate bringing elbows to the opposite knee in a pedaling motion.

exercises.name: Russian Twists
exercises.instructions: Sit with legs raised and twist your torso to each side.

exercises.name: Jump Squats
exercises.instructions: Perform a squat and then jump explosively, landing softly.

exercises.name: Tricep Dips
exercises.instructions: Lower your body using your arms behind you on a stable surface, then push back up.

exercises.name: Wall Sit
exercises.instructions: Sit against a wall with knees at 90 degrees and hold the position.

exercises.name: High Knees
exercises.instructions: Run in place while lifting your knees as high as possible.

exercises.name: Glute Bridge
exercises.instructions: Lie on your back, lift your hips while squeezing your glutes.

exercises.name: Superman
exercises.instructions: Lie on your stomach and lift arms and legs simultaneously.

exercises.name: Side Plank
exercises.instructions: Balance on one forearm and the side of one foot while keeping your body straight.

exercises.name: Step-ups
exercises.instructions: Step onto a bench with one foot and push up to standing, then step down.

exercises.name: Leg Raises
exercises.instructions: Lie flat and lift your legs to 90 degrees, then slowly lower.

exercises.name: Donkey Kicks
exercises.instructions: On all fours, kick one leg up and back, squeezing the glute.

exercises.name: Arm Circles
exercises.instructions: Extend arms and make small circles, gradually increasing in size.
